soot.dexpler

Class DexReturnPacker

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.Transformer
      • soot.BodyTransformer
        • soot.dexpler.DexReturnPacker

  • public class DexReturnPacker
extends BodyTransformer
    This transformer is the inverse of the DexReturnInliner. It looks for unnecessary duplicates of return statements and removes them.
